interesting is this, he says that a group of them were sent out in a craft to go scout out

01:12:37.360 --> 01:12:43.160
a new world that they could possibly develop as a habitation for themselves because Mars

01:12:43.160 --> 01:12:50.000
was no longer a planet on which they could survive. Right. And this scout ship runs into a planet

01:12:50.000 --> 01:13:00.100
where there are constant electrical storms. Uh, it's the opposite of Mars, but in a way that's also

01:13:00.100 --> 01:13:04.600
difficult to support human life. In other words, it's overgrown with vegetation, right? It's an

01:13:04.600 --> 01:13:13.000
incredibly volatile, but living planet. And they, they're like, we can't live in this planet under

01:13:13.000 --> 01:13:21.980
these conditions. We would have to modify this planet to live there. And so I suspect that what's

01:13:21.980 --> 01:13:29.620
going on there is the scouting out of a primordial earth by people from Mars, which then brings us to

01:13:29.620 --> 01:13:35.320
the question of the moon, you know, and what the moon is, right? I mean, so we've got Carl Wolf telling

01:13:35.320 --> 01:13:39.100
us there's a city on the dark side of the moon. We've got Ingo Swan having done remote viewing that

01:13:39.100 --> 01:13:43.940
confirms that. But I think that the situation with the moon is, is actually a lot more disturbing than

01:13:43.940 --> 01:13:48.640
there simply being, you know, a city sized alien base on the backside of the alien, whatever

01:13:48.640 --> 01:13:55.220
base on the backside of the moon. You look at the, the geometry and the mathematics of, of the moon

01:13:55.220 --> 01:14:01.740
in relation to the earth and the sun, it makes no sense. The moon is one four hundredth the distance

01:14:01.740 --> 01:14:07.800
between the earth and the sun. And it's one four hundredth the size of the sun. And so that creates

01:14:07.800 --> 01:14:14.780
these perfect eclipses that we see, right? That by itself is very odd. And then you look

01:14:14.780 --> 01:14:21.820
at the fact that the craters on the moon are all only a few miles deep. You never find a

01:14:21.820 --> 01:14:25.500
crater on the moon that's more than five or six miles deep. But some of these craters are

01:14:25.500 --> 01:14:34.400
like 186 miles wide, right? So, and at the, you know, the base of the largest craters, you

01:14:34.400 --> 01:14:39.780
see a convex surface. In other words, it looks nothing like the Grand Canyon or the Valles

01:14:39.780 --> 01:14:44.300
Marineris on Mars, where like, you know, an asteroid would hit it and you'd see a deep gouge

01:14:44.300 --> 01:14:51.780
that should be proportionally as deep as it is wide. No. What you're seeing apparently is a hard

01:14:51.780 --> 01:14:58.500
shell that's being revealed through the impact against the regolith by whatever object is. The

01:14:58.500 --> 01:15:06.040
ejecta is going 186 miles out in every direction, but there's never a crater deeper than a few

01:15:06.040 --> 01:15:11.500
miles. And what's being revealed there at the crater base is a hard convex surface.

01:15:12.260 --> 01:15:18.320
Then there's the impact. Well, one of them was a test. One of them was accidental. The first one,

01:15:18.880 --> 01:15:24.160
I think part of an Apollo lander hit the moon and there was a seismograph that had already been

01:15:24.160 --> 01:15:33.740
positioned there. And it registered basically the seismic signature that you would face if you were

01:15:33.740 --> 01:15:42.040
measuring a hollow object. That basically the reverberations went down for about 20 miles

01:15:42.040 --> 01:15:48.080
and then they stopped. And the way that the reverberation was distributed throughout the moon

01:15:48.080 --> 01:15:55.040
suggested that as the observers, you know, put it, it rang like a bell. And so then they repeated this

01:15:55.040 --> 01:16:01.340
test deliberately a second time, I think it was an Apollo 13. And this time they hit it with a more

01:16:01.340 --> 01:16:06.580
significant impact. And this kind of seismic signature was observed for three hours, the moon

01:16:06.580 --> 01:16:14.540
basically ringing like a hollow object for three hours. So there's all this evidence that the moon is

01:16:14.540 --> 01:16:18.720
an artificial satellite. And setting this in the context of Joe McMonigle's remote viewing of Mars,

01:16:18.960 --> 01:16:26.780
what I argue in closer encounters is that the people on Mars probably constructed the moon

01:16:26.780 --> 01:16:35.980
for two purposes. One, as a very large scale transport of a significant population from Mars to the orbit

01:16:35.980 --> 01:16:45.260
of the Earth. And two, as a terraforming device to radically alter the ecological situation of the

01:16:45.260 --> 01:16:50.320
planet so as to make it habitable for humans, right? They said there were these horrendous constant

01:16:50.320 --> 01:16:55.840
electrical storms and volcanic eruptions and so on and so forth. Well, you know, the Earth spun a lot

01:16:55.840 --> 01:17:01.400
faster before the, if the moon had not been in orbit at some point, we would have been dealing with a

01:17:01.400 --> 01:17:07.840
planet that was a lot more unstable, spinning much faster, prone to toppling over. The moon acts as a

01:17:07.840 --> 01:17:11.700
tremendous stabilizer for the Earth. By the way, that's another thing about the moon is that it has

01:17:11.700 --> 01:17:17.620
a unusually stable orbit as compared to the moons around other planets, as if there's a stabilizer

01:17:17.620 --> 01:17:23.100
inside of it. So I think it was created to transport a large population and it was used as a terraforming

01:17:23.100 --> 01:17:30.340
device. Now, to answer your deeper question, what does that say about who these people are,

01:17:30.340 --> 01:17:37.360
right? Number one, it says that they're people. So NHI is not an appropriate appellation for these

01:17:37.360 --> 01:17:45.780
individuals, right? They look like us, particularly they look Nordic, and they appear to have been the

01:17:45.780 --> 01:17:50.020
progenitors of the human race. Not only that, they appear to have terraformed the Earth to make it

01:17:50.020 --> 01:17:57.780
habitable for humanoids. But I have one huge problem with all of that. The time scales.

01:17:57.780 --> 01:18:05.320
It makes no sense whatsoever to me that you would have people who look like us,

01:18:05.800 --> 01:18:12.780
I don't know, millions of years BC on Mars. The same people

01:18:12.780 --> 01:18:21.660
are basically, you know, I don't know, involved in the power struggle that's been remembered as the

01:18:21.660 --> 01:18:28.480
myth of the Atlantean revolt. The same people are being encountered today by, let's say, Travis Walton

01:18:28.480 --> 01:18:36.220
when Walton was abducted. First, he had to deal with these greys, these little robotic entities

01:18:36.220 --> 01:18:40.940
that, you know, tried to put him back together after he, you know, sustained some kind of physical

01:18:40.940 --> 01:18:46.280
damage being thrown by the, you know, electrogravitic repulsion of the craft. But then he, you know,

01:18:46.280 --> 01:18:50.360
big strapping fellow that he was, he broke free of the control of these robots and the

01:18:50.360 --> 01:18:54.240
medical facility or whatever went down the hallway and he bumped into these Nordics.

01:18:54.660 --> 01:18:59.080
And from there on, he was handled by these people. He said they looked like they could

01:18:59.080 --> 01:19:00.640
all have been members of the same family.

01:19:00.720 --> 01:19:06.120
I went into another room where there was a chair. There was some kind of a projection or

01:19:06.120 --> 01:19:12.740
some kind of a viewing thing in this room where you could see a map of stars. A man came in

01:19:12.740 --> 01:19:20.720
while I was trying to find a way out there. And this was a human looking person. They had

01:19:20.720 --> 01:19:27.660
passed in a crowd, this individual, and on earth. He was bigger than me, taller and more muscular,

01:19:28.200 --> 01:19:39.040
very large individual. I went up and tried to talk to this guy and he didn't answer me. He led me

01:19:39.040 --> 01:19:46.040
outside of this craft that I was in, which was apparently parked inside of a large room or

01:19:46.040 --> 01:19:53.760
building or a larger craft and led me out of this room into another room where some other beings like

01:19:53.760 --> 01:20:05.040
himself put me unconscious. When I regained consciousness, I found myself laying on the

01:20:05.040 --> 01:20:11.780
roadway that I saw a craft hovering there that just sat there for a second and just shot straight

01:20:11.780 --> 01:20:15.260
up. That's the last I've seen of.

01:20:15.720 --> 01:20:24.220
And then you have cases like, you know, Betty, Andreas, and Luca, where, again, you have her

01:20:24.220 --> 01:20:31.240
taken, she's frozen together with her family by grays who come into the house. This is a 1960s

01:20:31.240 --> 01:20:42.600
housewife. And her and her daughter, Becky, I believe, were both taken. And initially they're

01:20:42.600 --> 01:20:48.200
handled by the grays who frees the, you know, the family and abduct them from the home. But then

01:20:48.200 --> 01:20:57.100
they are brought to a place where they encounter these angelic looking Nordic beings who proceed to

01:20:57.100 --> 01:21:03.460
tell Betty that essentially they're the angels and that the little grays are responsible for

01:21:03.460 --> 01:21:09.720
writing down all the deeds of humans. They're like a mass surveillance system that keeps a record of

01:21:09.720 --> 01:21:15.960
everybody's life. And these tall angelic beings told her that they brought Christ into the world

01:21:15.960 --> 01:21:21.220
and don't worry, they're going to bring him back again soon. And while she was with them, and by the

01:21:21.220 --> 01:21:26.000
way, she didn't say they took her into space. They seem to have taken her somewhere underground or

01:21:26.000 --> 01:21:32.420
underwater. And while she was there, she noticed this like doorway or large mirror or something

01:21:32.420 --> 01:21:40.080
that led toward this light. And some of these little gray entities went into the light and they

01:21:40.080 --> 01:21:45.600
told her, you can't go in there. That's the one, that's the source. And that sent Jesus into the

01:21:45.600 --> 01:21:51.660
world and will again soon, right? So a couple of points I want to make through, you know, these various

01:21:51.660 --> 01:22:00.540
cases. One is that we often hear these narratives where these, you know, tall statuesque, beautiful

01:22:00.540 --> 01:22:05.860
Nordics are pitted against these ugly little transhumanist gray robots. And, you know, like

01:22:05.860 --> 01:22:10.080
the Eisenhower story that, you know, Eisenhower met with the Nordics first and then, you know, he met

01:22:10.080 --> 01:22:13.960
with the grays and the grays made him a better deal because the Nordics wanted us to get rid of our

01:22:13.960 --> 01:22:17.500
nuclear weapons. The grays said, no, we'll give you our technology. Just let us abduct a certain number of

01:22:17.500 --> 01:22:23.960
people each year. This is extremely dubious to me, this narrative, because there are plenty of cases

01:22:23.960 --> 01:22:30.380
that attest to the fact that the grays are some kind of a cybernetic robot that work for these

01:22:30.380 --> 01:22:38.180
Nordics. And the Nordics appear to be the ones in control. So if there's a narrative that's being

01:22:38.180 --> 01:22:46.180
promulgated of, you know, beneficent Nordics versus like inhuman monstrous grays, I think it's some kind of

01:22:46.180 --> 01:22:47.080
good cop, bad cop.

01:22:47.500 --> 01:22:53.440
Bait and switch that's being set up here to ultimately put us in a position of

01:22:53.440 --> 01:23:01.540
captivation. And you first see this in 1950s Italy. There's a case that I cover in Closer

01:23:01.540 --> 01:23:10.380
Encounters. This guy, Bruno Samaciccia and his associates were engaged by these Nordics who had

01:23:10.380 --> 01:23:17.740
underground bases. And they claimed, first of all, as you see with all these cases of encounters with

01:23:17.740 --> 01:23:23.060
Nordics, demonstration of tremendous psi abilities. These Nordics are all telepathic. They can perform,

01:23:23.200 --> 01:23:29.640
you know, impressive telekinetic feats and so on and so forth. But what this Bruno Samaciccia and his

01:23:29.640 --> 01:23:34.080
associates said is that these Nordics were so benevolent, like they would never harm a fly.

01:23:34.080 --> 01:23:39.680
But they told us that there were these other entities, the Contrari, the CTR, the Contrari,

01:23:40.020 --> 01:23:45.700
who are these little robotic entities. And they're soulless. And they just want to, you know,

01:23:45.760 --> 01:23:52.100
they want control over the human soul because they don't have souls themselves. And they're locked in a

01:23:52.100 --> 01:23:58.040
millennial battle with these beings. So this Nordics versus Grey narrative goes all the way back to the

01:23:58.040 --> 01:24:07.840
1950s. Interestingly, Samaciccia makes a little note that, you know, at one point it occurred to me that the SS

01:24:07.840 --> 01:24:15.120
were involved in eugenics programs and there were rumors that after the war, these eugenics programs were

01:24:15.120 --> 01:24:21.160
continued in secret in underground facilities and so on and so forth. And I wonder whether these people that we saw,

01:24:21.160 --> 01:24:28.700
and they also saw very young people fitting this Nordic type, were basically products, outcomes of

01:24:28.700 --> 01:24:34.060
such programs that had begun in the Second World War. He engages, albeit briefly, in that kind of

01:24:34.060 --> 01:24:46.620
speculation. So long story short, my point is that these people are integral to human history and to the

01:24:46.620 --> 01:24:51.640
development of human society. We're not dealing with something that's coming from the outside. And I'd be

01:24:51.640 --> 01:24:58.860
very suspicious of, you know, claims by, let's say, you know, George Adamski saying that so-and-so

01:24:58.860 --> 01:25:04.460
Furkan told him that he was from Mars, or George Van Tassel saying that he was dealing with Venusians,

01:25:04.700 --> 01:25:10.900
or Billy Meyer telling us about the, you know, beneficent Pleiadians who are going to come to save us all,

01:25:10.900 --> 01:25:18.180
right? These beings are incredibly deceptive. I mean, deception is part of their MO. Jacques Vallée

01:25:18.180 --> 01:25:24.500
picks up on this in the context of the fairy folklore of the Middle Ages. I mean, one very

01:25:24.500 --> 01:25:31.680
consistent thing that you see in encounters with the gentry, the elite fairies in Brittany and in

01:25:31.680 --> 01:25:36.180
Ireland and so on and so forth, is that the peasants know that these beings lie all the time. They lie all

01:25:36.180 --> 01:25:40.940
the time about everything. And they only call them the good folk, because otherwise they'll get pissed

01:25:40.940 --> 01:25:48.300
off and learn what they'll do to you. So I think we're dealing with a faction of humanity that's

01:25:48.300 --> 01:25:57.480
positioned itself as a sort of overlord or master caste above the common herd. And they have adopted

01:25:57.480 --> 01:26:03.940
all kinds of guises and disguises to, you know, strategically deceive us for the sake of the

01:26:03.940 --> 01:26:09.900
preservation of their control system. How do you answer the time scale question? So you were

01:26:09.900 --> 01:26:14.420
saying, you know, if you have millions of years ago, these, you know, beings that looked like us

01:26:14.420 --> 01:26:19.480
existed on Mars, and then you have, you know, greys acting as their sort of robotic little drone

01:26:19.480 --> 01:26:24.980
emissaries. How does that necessarily answer this question of, you know, time scale?

01:26:24.980 --> 01:26:35.620
So the biggest problem with UFO disclosure is that the zero point energy electrogravitic

01:26:35.620 --> 01:26:43.160
propulsion system is not just going to give you a craft that travels from New York to Australia in

01:26:43.160 --> 01:26:50.460
an hour, right? It's going to give you a flying time machine. So you remember in the 1950s, I believe

01:26:50.460 --> 01:26:56.340
you've covered the subject before. And I go into it in some depth in Closer Encounters. There were

01:26:56.340 --> 01:27:04.420
these newspaper articles quoting the chairman of Martin Aircraft, Lear Convair, saying that the G

01:27:04.420 --> 01:27:11.720
engines are coming, that we've cracked anti-gravity. And within a few years, at a cost comparable to the

01:27:11.720 --> 01:27:16.220
Manhattan Project, we can have industrial scale development of electrogravitic craft that will get

01:27:16.220 --> 01:27:21.340
you from New York to Australia in an hour. Here's the problem, though. What they didn't realize,

01:27:21.540 --> 01:27:27.600
and I think what was explained to them when they finally got the memo, is that these are flying time

